high_descs: Go straight to the TV, then turn left and straight until reaching the hallway, taking a right and then another right into the bedroom, approaching the bed.
Pick up the butterknife from the bed.
Walk around the apple to the bedstand.
Slice the apple on the bedstand.
Place the butterknife down on the shelf.
Pick up the apple slice.
Turn around and take the exit on the right, then go straight to the table far ahead, then left to get to the hallway, then left again down the hall and right into the sink.
Rinse the apple with water in the sink.
Exit how you came in, turn right and go straight until reaching the kitchen area on the right, and go towards the microwave in the corner.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed Apple slice in a Microwave.
